name: Kristina Krikava
text: Expect to get hung up on if you're not fast enough to order. Also do not get there brownie it's undercooked! How gross. I gave two stars because their pizza is better then dominos .

name: James Goodnight
text: Waited about an hour and 15 minutes on my delivery order that was estimated at 30 minutes. Store was out of boneless wings so I ended up with traditional, neither crust had flavoring on it that I ordered, one pizza was completely missing a topping (but still got charged for it), and the wrong sauce was on the wings. Very unimpressed.
